    <h1>Melatonin Gummies Side Effects: The Complete Safety Guide</h1>
    <p class="pg-sub">The most common side effects of melatonin gummies are morning drowsiness (15-20% of users), headache (7%), nausea (5%), and dizziness (4%). These effects are typically mild and dose-dependent — higher doses cause more side effects without improving sleep quality. Most side effects resolve when you reduce the dose or stop taking melatonin.</p>
