      <details class="fq"><summary>What is the safest dose of melatonin gummies?</summary><p>The safest effective dose is 0.5-1mg taken 1-2 hours before bed. Research shows doses as low as 0.3mg improve sleep onset, and higher doses do not proportionally improve sleep quality while increasing side effects. Most commercial gummies contain 2.5-5mg — significantly more than needed. Start with the lowest available dose.</p></details>
